desc: An event and floral collective | Wedding + Event designers, stylists, florists planners with an extensive range of prop hire and industry friends to bring your dreamscape or your blank canvas to life. Adelaide-based, worldwide availability.

layout.text: An Events + Floral Collective | From designing your wedding from beginning to end, creating bespoke flowers for your events, jumping into an on-the-day styling, simply providing a consultation to bring visions to life or hiring our unique props Moonchild Creative is your go-to for the ultimate creative outlet and inspiration hub for your next event.
